From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: wisemanjr4 <mitsuking2003@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 15:50:53 +0900
Subject: [PATCH] SuperVertex: RCT - add missing unsafe blocks, optimize hot
 path

Unsafe block denylist additions (prevent crashes/deadlocks):
- LiquidBlock: LavaFluid.randomTick -> getBlockState -> join -> deadlock
- MagmaBlock, BuddingAmethystBlock, MushroomBlock: cross-chunk read
- NetherPortalBlock: entity spawn (Bukkit event)
- IceBlock, NyliumBlock: callBlockFadeEvent (Bukkit)
- FarmBlock: isNearWater cross-chunk scan
- ChangeOverTimeBlock (copper): +/-4 Manhattan scan + handleBlockFormEvent
- PointedDripstoneBlock: multi-level scan + handleBlockFormEvent
- SaplingBlock: StructureGrowEvent (Bukkit)

Performance optimizations:
- isBlockSafeForRCT: replace 22 instanceof checks with boolean[]
  array lookup indexed by block registry ID (O(1) after init).
  initBlockSafetyCache() called at server startup.
- buildRegions: reuse static int[]/Long2IntOpenHashMap/Int2ObjectOpenHashMap
  buffers instead of allocating new ones every tick -> reduces GC.
- Early return in buildRegions when Union-Find yields single region,
  avoiding unnecessary list construction overhead.

